{"tid":1289461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門公園遊行說服廢老指南","createTime":"2019-07-06T06:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T06:36:26.000Z","uid":134141,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"151c8364ba6850aac2eacde2797eafaaae25872d","tid":1289461,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:03:52.000Z","msg":"今次我地既目的係要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">拉攏淺藍</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ：行得正企得正驚咩送中？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">引渡條列最擔心既係政治罪行 你將來真係失去哂所有言論集會投票自由既時候 你再反抗就已經太遲 因為送中惡法係唔會有機會比你反抗 香港已經安裝左45條智慧辨識燈柱 中共可以莫須有拉你翻去 行得正企得正都會出事 可能你樣衰少少阿爺話拉你就拉你  </span><br />\n<br />\nQ：最近香港發生d咩事<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 林鄭無視200萬人民意 林鄭記者會無視有四個年輕人以死明志 警察濫用權力 612放左150粒以上既催淚彈....(有幾多講幾多)</span><br />\n<br />\nQ：和平示威咪算 點解要拆爛哂d野？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">已經死左四個人喇 政府仲係繼續當睇唔到<br />\n生命會唔會貴得過幾塊玻璃？ 除左以武制暴政 我地仲可以做d咩 和平示威已經冇用</span><br />\n<br />\nQ：你地係咪收左錢搞事？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">暴動罪最高刑罰係10年 有冇人願意為坐10年收果少少錢？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ：點建你地係中國人但咁唔愛國<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地曾經係英國殖民地 為英式文化影響 香港不論係文化 政治 經濟 教育 貨幣 同內地都好有差別 所以身份認同上同中國人有分別係好正常 一國兩制係保障香港人可以避免中港兩地上既矛盾 而政府就不停收窄緊香港人既自由 壓抑我地既民族意識 <span style=\"color: red;\">每個人都有選擇自己身份既自由 我係香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ：香港邊有能力獨立到？又冇水又冇糧 咩都靠中國<br />\n香港有七成未發展用地 可以用作興建海水化淡廠 糧食可以發展農地振興本土農業 軍事上香港有一兆幾財政盈餘 有能力自行購買軍備 規定年輕人18歲一定要服一年兵役 經濟上香港係國際金融中心 絕對唔會冇錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立場：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地要表達自己係支持廢中廢老福利</span> 盡量企係佢地立場 廢中廢老剩係會理自己生果金夠唔夠多 我地支持全民退休 增加生果金 佢地已經會軟化 <br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">務求一定要說服佢地 大家加油</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPS 上面問題如有補充 歡迎提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e130dccba03d0b656604ad58d4e0894ee63a814d","tid":1289461,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0162a8162c4f00a8bb67cdf75355cc51e8db6f8","tid":1289461,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:04:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7f1ffd215b6b879bf0baa954885e88be0ebe9e","tid":1289461,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:05:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61c4095616a1844a1ed07417e2670320caf9794","tid":1289461,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:05:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7af3cbe58814d2b654f3359aa5a50859e916dd","tid":1289461,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:06:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701706d083e1f705dc8478cd98777babd5198bcc","tid":1289461,"uid":261332,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"好地地講乜鬼野獨立。<br />\n一講就全部中間派離你而去。"},{"pid":"0730db2cb9c43efdb87d288f9fa42711186bc031","tid":1289461,"uid":105353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf03c63eafe42e7e8481a02b701ef800258ce158","tid":1289461,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim